title: Rep. Max Rose, Mail-In Voting, GOP Stimulus

description:
Guests: Jennifer Jacobs, Bloomberg White House reporter, Jack Fitzpatrick, Bloomberg Government Congressional reporter, Washington Secretary of State Kim Wyman, Rep. Max Rose, a democrat representing New York's 11th congressional district, Matt Gorman, Vice President at Targeted Victory, and Max Burns, Democratic Strategist.
